reallyliebehindanincidentasapparentlysimpleasthis.
Malorytransformstheconventionalmotiftointegrateitfully
intothescenario:thehunter'sabsenceisnotheresimply
convenient,butdemonstratestheinterestwhichatonceallows
hismistresstohurthimandwhichcontributestoherdesireto
elope.Maloryusesthecommonmotiftocreateaminiature
psychologicaldramashowingcharacter,emotionandmotivationin
anepisodewithlittleornoimportancetothecourseofthemain
