isincharacter.Themotifbecomesmorethansimplyformulaicor
conventional:Palomidesexploitsawell-knowncharacteristicof
ÄTristram,fittinghistreacherytoTristram'sbehaviourand
givingtheepisodeplausibilityinmorethanjusttherealmof
