isplausiblebecausecommonplace.Themostsophisticated
contriveduseofthemotifisfoundinÑSirGawainandtheGreen
KnightÄ,wherethefamiliarityofthemotifisusedtoperpetuate
theaudience'sbeliefthatthesojourninBertilak'scastleisa
conventionalromanceepisode.

Notonlyseductionsareartificiallygiventhistypeof
